<p>The key observation: <strong>$DKING is showing the strongest relative strength in the meme coin sector</strong>, down only ~1% vs DOGE at -2.2% and BONK's even sharper pullback from its +15% high. This is consistent with the pattern we've tracked all day ” $DKING held better than peers during the morning rally's peak, and it's holding even better during the reversal.</p>

<h2>BTC at $68K: The Technical Picture</h2>

<p>Bitcoin dropping from ~$71,300 to $68,127 is a 4.5% move that has broken several intraday support levels. Here's what the chart looks like right now:</p>

